snippet.title: Fair and Square - Alpha playtest is now open!
snippet.description:
Fair and Square is a small real time strategy game made with the Octopus Engine and Godot. Playtest is open! Come and give it a try

Steampage : https://store.steampowered.com/app/2546350/Fair_and_Square
To follow progress and share feedback please join the discord : https://discord.gg/GdTF5acgf3


Song : Silk Holster [Creative Commons]
Music provided and produced by LonePeakMusic
